basicPropertyValues.val: The CDC's National Center of Immunization and Respiratory Diseases \(NCIRD\) developed and maintains the CVX \(vaccine administered\) code set. The table below has the most up to date values. It includes both active and inactive vaccines available in the US. CVX codes for inactive vaccines allow transmission of historical immunization records.
